### Common TaskYou commands

| Command | What it does |
|---------|-------------|
| `ty list` | List all tasks |
| `ty board` | Kanban board view |
| `ty create "title" --project <name> --type <type> --body "details"` | Create a task |
| `ty execute <id>` | Send task to an agent |
| `ty retry <id>` | Retry a blocked/failed task |
| `ty output <id>` | See what an agent produced |
| `ty close <id>` | Mark task as done |
| `ty sessions list` | See running agents |
| `ty sessions cleanup` | Clean up stale sessions |
| `ty daemon status` | Check if daemon is running |

